### **3) JOINING AN INVITED MEETING**

**Step 1:** Receive a meeting invitation from someone (via email or Webex)

**Step 2:** Copy the Webex meeting link from the invitation

**Step 3:** Open the NoteX app → select “Live Meeting”

**Step 4:** Paste the Webex meeting link into NoteX

**Step 5:** Wait 1–2 minutes for the Bot to join

**Step 6:** Click “Let in” to admit the Bot (if you are the Host or have permission)

**Step 7:** End the meeting when finished

**Step 8:** Open NoteX to view the Meeting Notes and Summary

**Notes**:

✅ The Bot can join at any time — before or after the scheduled start time.

✅ If the meeting Host does not join, the Bot will wait 5–6 minutes before automatically leaving the meeting.
